source: 发言人 说 , 世人 共 知 , 中国 的 发展 不仅 符合 13 亿 中国人民 的 根本利益 , 也 有利于 世界 的 繁荣 与 发展 .
ref: the spokesman noted that it is known to all the world that china's development is not only in the fundamental interests of the 1.3 billion chinese people but also beneficial to the world's prosperity and development .
cand: the spokesman said , the world , a total of 13 million , not only conforms to the development of the people's interests , but also conducive to world prosperity and development .
data: 发言人 说 , 世人 共 知 , 中国 的 发展 不仅 符合 13 亿 中国人民 的 根本利益 , 也 有利于 世界 的 繁荣 与 发展 . the spokesman said , the world , a total of 13 million , not only conforms to the development of the people's interests , but also conducive to world prosperity and development .
backTrans: The spokesman said that the world's 13 million people are not only in the interests of the people, but also conducive to the prosperity and development of the world.

source: 在 国际 政治 舞台上 , 中国 是 一个 负责任 的 国家 , 对 维护 世界和平 与 稳定 发挥 了 积极 和 建设性 的 作用 .
ref: in the international political arena , china is a responsible country and has been playing an active and constructive role in safeguarding the world's peace and stability .
cand: in the international political arena , china is a responsible country that has contributed positively and constructively to uphold world peace and stability .
data: 在 国际 政治 舞台上 , 中国 是 一个 负责任 的 国家 , 对 维护 世界和平 与 稳定 发挥 了 积极 和 建设性 的 作用 . in the international political arena , china is a responsible country that has contributed positively and constructively to uphold world peace and stability .
backTrans: In the international political arena, China is a responsible country and has made positive and constructive contributions to the maintenance of world peace and stability.

source: 在 核 不 扩散 问题 上 , 中国 始终 严格 履行 有关 国际公约 , 坚决 反对 任何 形式 的 核扩散 , 主张 通过 协商 , 对话 和 加强 国际 监督 解决 这 类 问题 .
ref: on the issue of nuclear non-proliferation , china has always strictly abided by relevant international conventions , firmly opposed nuclear proliferation in any form , and insisted on solving such issues through negotiations , talks and the strengthening of international supervision .
cand: on the issue of non-proliferation of nuclear weapons , china has strictly enforced the international agreements and is opposed to any form of nuclear proliferation , and is advocating resolving these problems through negotiations , talks , and enhanced international monitoring .
data: 在 核 不 扩散 问题 上 , 中国 始终 严格 履行 有关 国际公约 , 坚决 反对 任何 形式 的 核扩散 , 主张 通过 协商 , 对话 和 加强 国际 监督 解决 这 类 问题 . on the issue of non-proliferation of nuclear weapons , china has strictly enforced the international agreements and is opposed to any form of nuclear proliferation , and is advocating resolving these problems through negotiations , talks , and enhanced international monitoring .
backTrans: On the issue of non-proliferation of nuclear weapons, China strictly enforces international agreements, opposes any form of nuclear proliferation, and advocates resolving these issues through negotiations, negotiations and strengthening international supervision.

source: 发言人 指出 , 令人 遗憾 的 是 , 海德 先生 无视 客观 事实 , 在 中美 关系 进一步 朝着 健康 , 稳定 发展 之 时 , 发表 这些 极 不 负责任 的 言论 , 完全 不 符合 中美 两 国 元首 不久 前 就 发展 两 国 关系 达成 的 共识 , 与 美国 社会 要求 加强 同 中国 的 合作 关系 的 主流 声音 背 道 而 弛 , 对 中美 关系 的 发展 无疑 是 有害 的 .
ref: the spokesman points out that it is regrettable that mr. hyde has turned a blind eye to the facts and made such extremely irresponsible remarks as sino-us relations are witnessing a healthy and stable development , which completely runs counter to the common grounds on the development of bilateral ties reached recently by heads of states of china and the us , goes against the mainstream voice in us asking to strengthen the cooperative relations with china , and is certainly harmful to the development of sino-us relations .
cand: the spokesman stated that it was regretful that mr. hyde ignored the objective facts and issued such irresponsible statements at a time when the sino-us relationship is heading towards healthy and stable progress . his statements contradicted the recent consensus in developing bilateral ties , reached by the state leaders of china and the u.s. they are running counter to the demand of mainstream u.s. society for enhancing the cooperative relationship with china , and will certainly harm the development of the sino-us relationship .
data: 发言人 指出 , 令人 遗憾 的 是 , 海德 先生 无视 客观 事实 , 在 中美 关系 进一步 朝着 健康 , 稳定 发展 之 时 , 发表 这些 极 不 负责任 的 言论 , 完全 不 符合 中美 两 国 元首 不久 前 就 发展 两 国 关系 达成 的 共识 , 与 美国 社会 要求 加强 同 中国 的 合作 关系 的 主流 声音 背 道 而 弛 , 对 中美 关系 的 发展 无疑 是 有害 的 . the spokesman stated that it was regretful that mr. hyde ignored the objective facts and issued such irresponsible statements at a time when the sino-us relationship is heading towards healthy and stable progress . his statements contradicted the recent consensus in developing bilateral ties , reached by the state leaders of china and the u.s. they are running counter to the demand of mainstream u.s. society for enhancing the cooperative relationship with china , and will certainly harm the development of the sino-us relationship .
backTrans: The spokesman said that as China-U.S. relations move towards healthy and stable development, Mr. Hyde ignored objective facts and made such irresponsible remarks. His remarks run counter to the consensus reached recently between the leaders of China and the United States on the development of bilateral relations, violate the demands of the mainstream American society to strengthen cooperation with China, and will certainly harm the development of China-U.S. relations.

source: 中国 最 大规模 的 海水 淡化 工程 落户 舟山
ref: china's largest seawater desalination project to be kicked off in zhoushan
cand: china's largest seawater desalination project begins in zhoushan
data: 中国 最 大规模 的 海水 淡化 工程 落户 舟山 china's largest seawater desalination project begins in zhoushan

source: 新华社 杭州 12 月 6 日 电 ( 潘 一 峰 许 群 ) 迄今为止 中国 内地 规模 最 大 , 日 处理 量 达 1 万 吨 的 海水 淡化 工程 , 将 落户 浙江省 舟山 市 普陀 区 .
ref: xinhua news agency report of december 6th from hangzhou ( by pan yifeng and xu qun ) - china's largest seawater desalination project in the mainland so far , with a daily production capacity of 10000 tons , is to be kicked off in the putuo district of zhoushan city in zhejiang province .
cand: hangzhou , december 6 ( xinhua ) -- a chinese mainland so far the largest on the handling capacity of 1 million tons of sea water desalination project , will be settled down in the zhejiang zhoushan po area .
data: 新华社 杭州 12 月 6 日 电 ( 潘 一 峰 许 群 ) 迄今为止 中国 内地 规模 最 大 , 日 处理 量 达 1 万 吨 的 海水 淡化 工程 , 将 落户 浙江省 舟山 市 普陀 区 . hangzhou , december 6 ( xinhua ) -- a chinese mainland so far the largest on the handling capacity of 1 million tons of sea water desalination project , will be settled down in the zhejiang zhoushan po area .
backTrans: Hangzhou, Dec. 6 Chinese mainland The largest 1 million tons of desalination project to date will be located in the Zhoushan District of Zhejiang Province.

source: 对于 深 受 缺 水 之 苦 的 舟山 居民 来 说 , 在 他们 身边 浩荡 了 千 百年 的 海水 即将 变成 清澈 甘 甜 的 自来水 流入 千家万户 .
ref: for residents in zhoushan long accustomed to water shortages , the seawater surging beside them for hundreds of thousands of years will soon become clean and sweet tap water running into thousands of homes .
cand: for zhoushan residents , who suffer greatly from water shortages , the vast and mighty seawater that has been flowing by their side for hundreds and thousands of years will soon become clear and sweet tap water that runs into tens of thousands of households .
data: 对于 深 受 缺 水 之 苦 的 舟山 居民 来 说 , 在 他们 身边 浩荡 了 千 百年 的 海水 即将 变成 清澈 甘 甜 的 自来水 流入 千家万户 . for zhoushan residents , who suffer greatly from water shortages , the vast and mighty seawater that has been flowing by their side for hundreds and thousands of years will soon become clear and sweet tap water that runs into tens of thousands of households .
backTrans: For Zhoushan residents who suffer greatly from water shortages, the vast and powerful waters of hundreds and thousands of years will soon become clear and sweet tap water, flowing through thousands of homes.

source: 记者 从 有关部门 获悉 , 国家 海洋 局 杭州 水处理 技术 开发 中心 与 舟山 市 普陀 区 六 横 镇 政府 于 日前 签署 了 万 吨 海水 淡化 工程 合作 协议 .

cand: the relevant department , the hangzhou water treatment technology development center and zhoushan po town in six areas along the recently signed million tons of sea water desalination project cooperation agreement .

source: 全市 共有 大小 岛屿 1390 个 , 人 均 淡水 拥有 量 为 601 立方 米 , 仅 为 浙江省 人 均 拥有 量 的 25.4%, 吃水 问题 一直 困扰 着 这个 海岛 城市 居民 的 生活 .
ref: the entire city consists of 1390 islands . the per capita fresh water is 601 cubic meters , which equals to only 25.4% of the per capita average in zhejiang province . the problem of drinking water shortages has long plagued residents of the island city .
cand: there are 1390 islands of varying sizes in the city . on average , each person has 601 cubic meters of fresh water , only 25.4 percent of that of zhejiang province . drinking water has always been a problem that affects the residents ' lives in this island city .

source: 由 国家 海洋 局 杭州 水处理 技术 开发 中心 负责 开发 的 反 渗透 海水 淡化 技术 , 是 一种 以 压力 为 驱 动力 的 膜 分离 过程 , 是 当今 国际 海水 淡化 研究 领域 的 热 点 .
ref: the technique of seawater desalination by reverse osmosis , developed by the hangzhou development center of water treatment technology under the state oceanic administration , is a process of membrane separation through the driving force of pressure , which at present is a focal point for current global seawater desalination research .
cand: the reverse osmosis seawater desalination technology developed by hangzhou development center of water treatment technology under the state oceanic administration is a membrane diffusion process powered by pressure and is the focus in today's international seawater desalination research domain .

backTrans: The reverse osmosis desalination technology developed by the Water Treatment Technology Development Center of the State Oceanic Administration is a pressure-driven membrane diffusion process, which is the focus of international desalination research.

source: 新华社 布达佩斯 12 月 5 日 电 ( 记者 刘 为 民 ) 匈牙利 5 日 就 全国 公共 卫生 医疗 机构 的 私有 化 和 境 外 匈 族人 的 双重国籍 问题 举行 了 全民 公决 投票 .
ref: xinhua news agency report of december 5th from budapest ( by staff reporter liu weimin ) - a national referendum was held on the 5th in hungary on issues regarding the privatization of the country's hospitals and public health-care institutions and the granting of dual citizenship to ethnic hungarians living outside the country .

source: 匈牙利 全国 选举 办公室 5 日 深夜 对 99.91% 的 选票 进行 的 统计 结果 显示 ,301.1 万 人 参加 了 投票 , 占 全国 选民 总数 的 37.48% .

source: 其中 191.9 万 人和 103.3 万 人 对 第 一个 问题 分别 投 了 赞成票 和 反对 票 , 占 全国 选民 人数 的 23.87% 和 12.85% ; 151.8 万 人和 142.6 万 人 对 第 二 个 问题 分别 投 了 赞成票 和 反对 票 , 占 全国 选民 人数 的 18.88% 和 17.75% .
ref: among them , 1919000 said " yes " and 1033000 said " no " to the first question , accounting for 23.87% and 12.85% respectively of the total number of voters across the country ; 1518000 and 1426000 voted for and against the second question , accounting for 18.88% and 17.75% respectively of the total number of voters across the country .
cand: these 191.9 million and 103.3 million respectively for the first issue cast a vote of the electorate and the amount 23.87% ; 151.8 million and 142.6 million respectively for the second issue cast a vote of the electorate 18.88% and 17.75% .
data: 其中 191.9 万 人和 103.3 万 人 对 第 一个 问题 分别 投 了 赞成票 和 反对 票 , 占 全国 选民 人数 的 23.87% 和 12.85% ; 151.8 万 人和 142.6 万 人 对 第 二 个 问题 分别 投 了 赞成票 和 反对 票 , 占 全国 选民 人数 的 18.88% 和 17.75% . these 191.9 million and 103.3 million respectively for the first issue cast a vote of the electorate and the amount 23.87% ; 151.8 million and 142.6 million respectively for the second issue cast a vote of the electorate 18.88% and 17.75% .

source: 根据 匈牙利 的 有关 法律 , 只有 参加 投票 的 人数 超过 全国 选民 总数 的 50%, 或者 对 上述 问题 投 赞成票 或 反对 票 的 人数 超过 全国 选民 总数 的 25%, 公决 结果 才 有效 .
ref: under hungary's relevant laws , a referendum result is valid only if the number of people taking part in the vote is more than 50% of the total number of voters across the nation or if the number of votes for or against the above questions exceed 25% of the total number of voters across the nation .
cand: according to hungarian laws , only the turnout of voters nationwide exceeded 50 per cent of the present and casting an affirmative or negative vote on the number of voters nationwide exceeding 25% of the referendum .
data: 根据 匈牙利 的 有关 法律 , 只有 参加 投票 的 人数 超过 全国 选民 总数 的 50%, 或者 对 上述 问题 投 赞成票 或 反对 票 的 人数 超过 全国 选民 总数 的 25%, 公决 结果 才 有效 . according to hungarian laws , only the turnout of voters nationwide exceeded 50 per cent of the present and casting an affirmative or negative vote on the number of voters nationwide exceeding 25% of the referendum .
backTrans: According to Hungarian law, only the national voter turnout exceeds the current 50 per cent, and more than 25 per cent of the country's voters voted yes or no in the referendum.

backTrans: The Andean Community Government must therefore strive to find and establish effective mechanisms to lift it out of poverty, strengthen the participation of people in State affairs and promote social stability and development.

ref: toledo pointed out that although many issues need to be resolved in the andean community , latin america integration over the last few years has witnessed much progress . the establishment of the south american community will be announced here on the 8th at the 3rd south american leaders ' summit .
cand: toledo noted that , despite the many problems that required resolving within the andean community , the latin american integration process has achieved tremendous progress in recent years . the establishment of the south american community will be announced at the third south american state leaders meeting to be held here on the 8th .
data: 托 莱 多 指出 , 尽管 安 共 体 内部 有 不少 问题 有待 解决 , 但 近年来 拉 美 一体 化 进程 取得 了 很 大 进展 , 南美 共同体 将 于 8 日 在 这里 举行 的 第 三 届 南美 国家 首脑 会议 上 宣布 建立 . toledo noted that , despite the many problems that required resolving within the andean community , the latin american integration process has achieved tremendous progress in recent years . the establishment of the south american community will be announced at the third south american state leaders meeting to be held here on the 8th .
backTrans: Toledo noted that, despite the many problems within the Andean Community that needed to be addressed, the process of Latin American integration had made great progress in recent years. The establishment of the South American Community will be announced at the 3rd Meeting of Leaders of South American Countries held here on the 8th.

backTrans: According to a senior official of the Yangtze River Three Gorges Project Development Corporation. The underground power station of the Three Gorges Dam is located in the mountains to the right of the dam. Its main structures include water towers, drainage canals, active forces, tailwater systems, vertical shafts and 500 kV substations.

data: 新华社 北京 12 月 8 日 电 ( 记者 黄 富 慧 ) 中国 道路 运输 协会 会长 姚 明 德 8 日 在 此间 举行 的 一个 新闻 发布 会 上 , 对 设立 中国 航海 节 表示 " 充满 了 信心 " . xinhua news agency , beijing , december 8 ( reporter huang fuhui ) yao mingde , chairman of the china road transport association , expressed at a press conference held here on the 8th that he was " very confident " that a china nautical fair will be established .

source: 同时 担任 郑和 下 西洋 600 周年纪念 活动 筹备 领导 小组 办公室 主任 的 姚 明 德 说 , 包括 交通部 在 内 的 16 个 筹备 领导 小组 成员 部门 已经 全部 同意 把 每 年 的 7 月 11 日 , 即 郑和 第 一次 下 西洋 的 日子 定 为 中国 的 航海 节 , 将 向 国家 建议 设立 此 节日 .
ref: yao mingde , who is also the director of the leadership working group preparing commemorative activities marking the 600th anniversary of zheng he's first voyage to the west , said that the 16 departments of the preparatory panel including the ministry of communications have all agreed that july 11th of each year , the date zheng he started his first voyage to the west , will become china's navigation festival and a proposal will be raised the state for introducing it .
cand: yao mingde , who was also the chairman of the office of the organizing leading group of zheng he's 600 anniversaries to the west commemorative activities , stated that 16 organizing leading groups including the ministry of transportation had all agreed to set every july 11 , the day of zheng he's first expedition to the west , as the nautical fair in china and will suggest that the state establish such a fair .
data: 同时 担任 郑和 下 西洋 600 周年纪念 活动 筹备 领导 小组 办公室 主任 的 姚 明 德 说 , 包括 交通部 在 内 的 16 个 筹备 领导 小组 成员 部门 已经 全部 同意 把 每 年 的 7 月 11 日 , 即 郑和 第 一次 下 西洋 的 日子 定 为 中国 的 航海 节 , 将 向 国家 建议 设立 此 节日 . yao mingde , who was also the chairman of the office of the organizing leading group of zheng he's 600 anniversaries to the west commemorative activities , stated that 16 organizing leading groups including the ministry of transportation had all agreed to set every july 11 , the day of zheng he's first expedition to the west , as the nautical fair in china and will suggest that the state establish such a fair .
backTrans: Yao Mingde, who is also the director of the leadership group for Zheng He's 600th anniversary, said that 16 leading groups, including the Ministry of Transport, have agreed to make Zheng He's first expedition to the west on July 11 each year as part of the China Sailing Expo and to recommend that the country set up such an expo.

data: 从 1405 年 到 1433 年 的 28 年间 , 郑和 率领 200 多 艘 船队 和 近 3 万 人 , 先后 7 次 远 渡 重 洋 , 经 东南亚 , 印度洋 到达 红海 和 非洲 , 行程 30 多 万 公里 , 走 遍 亚 非 30 多 个 国家 和 地区 . in the 28 years between 1405 and 1433 , zheng he led more than 200 fleets and close to 30000 people to cross the vast ocean seven times through southeast asia and the indian ocean to the red sea and africa , sailing more than 300000 kilometers and visited over 30 countries and regions in asia and africa .

He urged the parties to seize this opportunity to ensure "real progress" in the peace process in preparation for the October 2005 elections.

source: 新华社 西安 12 月 9 日 电 ( 记者 刘 喜 梅 ) " 国际 计划 " 国家 主管 詹 姆 斯 ・ 莫 瑞 与 陕西省 环保 局 局长 何 发 理 9 日 在 西安 签署 合作 协议 , 即日 起 国际 计划 中国 " 供水 与 环境卫生 " 项目 将 正式 与 陕西省 " 绿色 文明 示范 工程 " 合作 , 推动 和 帮助 陕西省 农村 人 畜 饮水 工程 , 沼气 建设 , 健康 教育 等 项目 的 实施 .
ref: xinhua news agency report of december 9th from xi ' an ( by staff reporter liu ximei ) - the country director of " plan international " , james mori , signed a cooperation agreement with the director of the shaanxi provincial environmental protection bureau , he fali , on the 9th in xi ' an . from now on , plan international's china " water supply and environmental sanitation " program will formally join hands with shaanxi province's " green culture model project " to push forward and help the implementation of projects such as rural drinking water for people and animals , construction of methane facilities and health education .

backTrans: Xinhua News Agency, Xi'an, December 9 (Reporter Liu Ximei) Shaanxi Provincial Planning State Bureau Director James Morey and Shaanxi Provincial Environmental Protection Bureau Director He Fari signed a cooperation agreement in Xi'an on the 9th. The International Plan "Water Supply and Sanitation" project will officially cooperate with the "Green Civilization Demonstration Project" in Shaanxi Province to promote and assist in the implementation of projects including the Shanxi Village Human and Livestock Drinking Water Project, the development of biogas facilities, and health education.

backTrans: The project and the International Plan for China's Water Supply and Sanitation Project in Shaanxi Province will promote water sanitation cooperation in poor rural areas of Shaanxi Province and build "green villages" and "green school projects" in poor areas to complement each other's strengths and promote sustainable development.

source: 新华社 上海 12 月 13 日 电 ( 记者 刘 丹 ) 13 日 在 上海 闭幕 的 " 中国 青少年 社会 教育 论坛 ─ ─ 2004 ・ 媒体 与 未成年人 发展 " 倡议 : 中国 应 建立 有关 未成年人 状况 的 新闻 发言人 制度 , 定期 就 未成年人 发展 现状 和 存在 的 问题 发布 消息 .
ref: xinhua news agency report of december 13th from shanghai ( by reporter liu dan ) - " the china youth social education forum 2004 media and the development of minors " , which ended on the 13th in shanghai , has proposed that china should introduce a spokesman system in respect of the status of minors to regularly release news on the current development and existing problems of minors .

backTrans: XINHUA News Agency, Shanghai, December 13 (Reporter Liu Dan) 13 in Shanghai closed the "2004 China Youth Social Education Forum - Media and Minors Development Forum" suggested that China should establish a system of press spokespersons related to the situation of minors, regularly publish information on the status of the development of minors and problems encountered.

source: 上海 市 有关方面 最近 进行 的 一 项 调查 显示 , 未成年人 平均 每人 每天 看 课外 书籍 1.17 小时 , 看 电视 1.05 小时 , 上 网 0.99 小时 … … 在 未成年人 课余 时间 安排 上 , 有 一半 左右 的 时间 是 与 媒体 一起 度过 的 , 媒体 正 以 一种 全新 的 社会 力量 , 成为 影响 未成年人 成长 和 发展 不可忽视 的 因素 .
ref: a recent poll conducted by the relevant organizations in shanghai showed that minors spend an average of 1.17 , 1.05 and 0.99 hours each day on extracurricular books , tv and the internet . about half of their after-school time is spent on the media , which , as a brand-new social force , has become a factor that can't be neglected in minors ' growth and development .
cand: a recent survey conducted by relevant shanghai authorities showed that minors spend an average of 1.17 hours per day reading leisure books , 1.05 hours watching television , 0.99 hours surfing the internet about half of the arrangements for minors ' after-school time involve the media . the media has become a factor affecting the growth and development of minors with an entirely new social force that cannot be ignored .

backTrans: According to a recent survey conducted by the Shanghai authorities, minors spend an average of 1.17 hours a day reading leisure books, 1.05 hours watching TELEVISION, 0.99 hours surfing the Internet, and about half of their after-school schedule involves the media. The media has become a factor affecting the growth and development of minors, and it is a brand-new social force that can not be ignored.

data: ( 国际 ) 伊拉克 外长 认为 伊 大选 面临 三 大 问题 iraqi foreign minister ( international ) said that three major issues facing elections
backTrans: Iraq's Foreign Minister (International) said the elections faced three major problems

source: 新华社 迪 拜 ( 阿 联 酋 ) 12 月 14 日 电 ( 记者 邢 旭东 燕 毅 ) 伊拉克 临时政府 外长 泽 巴里 14 日 在 迪 拜 说 , 伊拉克 明年 1 月 30 日 举行 的 大选 将 面临 三 大 问题 , 即 : 安全局势 恶化 阻碍 和 干扰 选举 进程 ; 选民 担心 遭 恐怖 袭击 不 敢 投票 而 影响 投票 率 ; 如何 最 大 程度 地 保障 选举 的 透明度 和 公正 性 .
ref: xinhua news agency report of december 14th from dubai ( the united arab emirates ) ( by staff reporters xing xudong and yan yi ) - the iraqi interim government's foreign minister zebari said on the 14th in dubai that the general election scheduled for january 30th next year would face three major problems , namely a deterioration of the security situation hampering and disturbing the election process ; an influence in voter turnout due to worries of terrorist attacks , and how to best ensure the transparency and fairness of the election .
cand: new dubai ( uae ) , december 14 ( xinhua ) -- the iraqi government since prime minister milos bari 14 in dubai said that iraq held on 30 january , the general elections will face three major issues : the security situation deteriorated obstruction and interference in the electoral process ; that the terrorist attack on voters to cast ballots and impact ; how to maximize the protection of the transparency and impartiality .
data: 新华社 迪 拜 ( 阿 联 酋 ) 12 月 14 日 电 ( 记者 邢 旭东 燕 毅 ) 伊拉克 临时政府 外长 泽 巴里 14 日 在 迪 拜 说 , 伊拉克 明年 1 月 30 日 举行 的 大选 将 面临 三 大 问题 , 即 : 安全局势 恶化 阻碍 和 干扰 选举 进程 ; 选民 担心 遭 恐怖 袭击 不 敢 投票 而 影响 投票 率 ; 如何 最 大 程度 地 保障 选举 的 透明度 和 公正 性 . new dubai ( uae ) , december 14 ( xinhua ) -- the iraqi government since prime minister milos bari 14 in dubai said that iraq held on 30 january , the general elections will face three major issues : the security situation deteriorated obstruction and interference in the electoral process ; that the terrorist attack on voters to cast ballots and impact ; how to maximize the protection of the transparency and impartiality .
backTrans: DUBAI, Dec. 14 (Xinhua Li Yawen) Iraqi Government Prime Minister Milos Bari said in Dubai on the 14th, Iraq's January 30 general election will face three major problems: the deterioration of the security situation and interference with the electoral process; Impact on the voting of voters in terrorist attacks; How to maximize transparency and fairness.

source: 泽 巴里 在 迪 拜 举行 的 " 阿拉伯 战略 论坛 " 会议 上 发表 讲话 时 说 , 伊拉克 如期 举行 大选 是 非常 必要 的 , 因为 大选 不仅 确定 伊拉克 新 的 领导人 , 也 将 确定 伊拉克 是 属于 全体 伊拉克 人 的 自由 , 民主 和 统一 的 国家 .
ref: speaking at the " arab strategy forum " held in dubai , zebari said that it was essential for iraq to hold an election on schedule as the election would not only elect iraq's new leaders but would also certify the fact that iraq was a free , democratic and unified country belonging to all the iraqi people .
cand: when addressing the " arab strategy forum " in dubai , al-zebari said that it is of the utmost importance that iraq holds its election as scheduled , because not only will the election determine the new iraqi leader , it will also demonstrate that iraq is a free , democratic , and unified country that belongs to all iraqis .
data: 泽 巴里 在 迪 拜 举行 的 " 阿拉伯 战略 论坛 " 会议 上 发表 讲话 时 说 , 伊拉克 如期 举行 大选 是 非常 必要 的 , 因为 大选 不仅 确定 伊拉克 新 的 领导人 , 也 将 确定 伊拉克 是 属于 全体 伊拉克 人 的 自由 , 民主 和 统一 的 国家 . when addressing the " arab strategy forum " in dubai , al-zebari said that it is of the utmost importance that iraq holds its election as scheduled , because not only will the election determine the new iraqi leader , it will also demonstrate that iraq is a free , democratic , and unified country that belongs to all iraqis .
backTrans: Speaking at the Arab Strategic Forum in Dubai, Zebari said it was vital that Iraq hold elections as scheduled, which would not only determine Iraq's new leadership, but would also prove that Iraq is a free, democratic and united country that belongs to all Iraqis.

data: 科 斯 塔 说 , 与 2003 年 相比 , 阿富汗 今年 的 鸦片 种植 面积 增加 了 64%, 海洛因 产量 达到 500 多 吨 , 高于 全球 海洛因 黑市 一年 的 交易 量 , 这 一 趋势 意味 着 全球 毒品 纯度 提高 以及 吸 毒死 亡 人数 相应 增加 . costa said that compared to 2003 , opium cultivation in afghanistan this year increased by 64% and heroin production reached more than 500 tons per year , higher than the global heroin market transaction volume , which means that the global drug purity and a corresponding increase in drug poisoning .
backTrans: This year, opium cultivation in Afghanistan has increased by 64 percent compared to 2003, and heroin production has reached more than 500 tons per year, higher than the volume of the global heroin market, which means a corresponding increase in global drug purity and drug poisoning, Costa said.

data: 迄今 , 美国 已经 释放 了 约 200 名 关 塔 那 摩 囚犯 , 其中 一些 人 在 遣送 回国 后 被 释放 , 另 有 少数 人 在 回国 后 被 继续 关押 , 但 至少 有 12 人 被 释放 后 又 参与 了 打击 美军 的 活动 . to date , the united states has released approximately 200 guantanamo prisoners . after their return to their home countries , some of them were released , while a small number of them remain in prison , but at least 12 of them have taken part in fighting the u.s. army again after their release .
backTrans: So far, the United States has released about 200 Guantanamo detainees. When they returned to their countries, some of them were released, and a small number of them remained in prison, but at least 12 of them returned to fighting with U.S. forces after their release.
